# Legal BERT Classification

## Description

This project uses BERT model to classify legal texts into categories.

## Files

* legal_bert_classification.py: Main code
* performance_results.png: Model results

## How to run

1. Install required libraries
2. Run:
   python legal_bert_classification.py

## Model

This project is based on BERT (Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers).

